Oscar ENGELSTAD, Trustee in Bankruptcy of the Estate of David P. OSWALD and Nellie E. Oswald, His Wife, Bankrupts, Appellant, v. SECURITY NATIONAL BANK, a Corporation, Appellee. No. 7058. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. April 4, 1933.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and MACK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel, ordered appeal dismissed, without costs; mandate forthwith.
